results.title: Beautifully hand crafted 3 dimensional Intarsia Wood Art KITTY CAT Picture Photo Frame
results.description:
Beautifully hand-crafted 3-dimensional Intarsia KITTY CAT Wood Picture Photo Frame.

This piece of intarsia wood art required a lot of workmanship since it was hand-carved from 24 different pieces of wood with different thickness and glued together on a wood base to form this Kitty Cat Picture Frame.

Shelf display or wall hanging (the frame has a stand and also a hook on the back). 

All hand-carved using different kinds of wood to bring different colors for the piece. So, the colors of wood here are natural colors of wood. For this feature, it's almost like one-of-a-kind because next time if we make the same design again, it won't look exactly the same as the wood grain will change slightly. Also, each piece is hand-carved individually, so it's all unique. (The actual item you'll receive maybe very slightly different than what pictured since each piece is hand-crafted individually. However, we're confident you'll love the piece you receive regarding beauty and quality. We can confirm this because we have a lot of repeated happy customers).

Semi-gloss finish.

It would add a very beautiful & interesting item to your collection or make a perfect gift idea.....

Overall measurements : approximately 10.25" long X 7.75" high X 1" thick.

The frame measures approximately 7-3/8" high X 5.5" wide.

Photo area measures approximately 5-7/8" high X 3-7/8" wide.

Item # PF-Cat-1E

Hand crafted by B.Evans

Original Price : $100

Today Price : $49.95 . You save : $50

results.title: live laugh love deco mesh wreath, front door or wall, great gift for any occasion, mom Mothers day, housewarming gift, unique,one of a kind
results.description:
This is a very pretty deco mesh live laugh love with succulents wreath. Rustic farmhouse style. This is a pancake wreath that fits behind storm, screen doors. Would look great on front door or wall. Great gift for any occasion, housewarming,mom for Mothers day are just a few. Keeping for yourself is even better. This can be used all year, every season which is very nice.
     This is a very unique one of a kind wreath. Every one is handcrafted by me so no two are the same but can be similar.
     It is made of very pretty deco mesh in tan with metallic threading and blue plaid. Decorated with playful ribbons and burlap and lace. There are white and blue mesh curls. The sign is farmhouse wooden with live laugh and love inscribed. There are 3 succulents 2 are handprinted and the middle is faux green.
     If you enjoyed this wreath please check out the others I have made. Wax melts are coming soon. Thank you for stopping by.

results.title: Mosaic funky hearts
results.description:
With their unusual shape these funky colourful hearts make an original present.

Two are available: a red/ orangey one and a blue/teal one.

In both hearts I’ve hidden some cute creatures, including one of my favourite bugs: the ladybird, which as well as being a friend of all gardeners is also supposed to bring good luck in Italy.

The hearts are set on beech plywood.

To make them I have used different materials: glass and porcelain tiles, ceramic shapes, millefiori beads, Tiffany glass and  wooden buttons.

The back is painted black.

There is a hole at the top to hang them.

Other hearts are available. See picture and check listing.
